                maxAmountsInScaled18,
                params.minBptAmountOut,
                poolData.balancesLiveScaled18,
                params.userData
            ) == false
        ) {
            revert IVaultErrors.BeforeAddLiquidityHookFailed();
        }
        return true;
    }

